{"tid":2209076,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"維權出版人被拒保釋 美轟北京滅聲","createTime":"2020-09-19T11:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T11:23:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"51797d86f0242f5f8215a2b45cfa9a6cf8d86a67","tid":2209076,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:23:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200919/I6GAW5F5NZEARAKE7XY26HW3YA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200919%2FI6GAW5F5NZEARAKE7XY26HW3YA%2F&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxEyfe5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=48bc9b08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200919%2FI6GAW5F5NZEARAKE7XY26HW3YA%2F&h=4d2d22ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200919/I6GAW5F5NZEARAKE7XY26HW3YA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n維權出版人被拒保釋 美轟北京滅聲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GI2ivu4dcfQlfwy-gzUaPUtd1G4=/1181x796/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RCK7QTXY4RCNJBHLXKJVGMCMAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGI2ivu4dcfQlfwy-gzUaPUtd1G4%3D%2F1181x796%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRCK7QTXY4RCNJBHLXKJVGMCMAM.jpg&h=91a8c0ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■耿瀟男被捕11天仍未能見律師。<br />\n<br />\n中國文化出版人耿瀟男被北京公安帶走第11天，遭當局以涉嫌非法經營罪為名刑事拘留，律師為她申請保釋被拒。美國國務院昨天表示關注事件。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：直擊疫情實況 2月被警帶走  當局不起訴 拒放人 陳秋實遭監視居住<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台引述一名國務院官員表示，美方對耿瀟男夫婦被捕表示擔憂，會持續跟進案件，向相關人員追究責任，又指北京當局阻止他們會見律師，是試圖打壓異見聲音、限制言論自由。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多次被禁見律師<br />\n<br />\n北京莫少平律師事務所代表耿瀟男，周三收到北京市公安局海淀分局的通知書，指她不符合條件，不予「變更強制措施」，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n耿瀟男是中國天畫畫天影業的前行政總裁、瑞雅書業總編輯，多次聲援異見人士及知識分子，包括清華大學法學院前教授許章潤。本月9日她與丈夫秦真被指涉嫌「印刷、銷售非法出版物」的「非法經營罪」，遭警方刑事拘留至今。<br />\n<br />\n香港電台/自由亞洲電台"}]}